// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0880 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 8543c65e-aa90-56d4-91ed-6e67e31e1c52

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:1* OR ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
